Open Anaconda Prompt (Administrator)

Install nbConvert
  > pip install nbConvert[webPDF]

Install pandoc
  > conda install -c conda-forge pandoc
  
Install pyppeteer
  > puppeteer-install
  
Open your notebook -> File -> Download as -> PDF via Html (.pdf)

Voila!! Your pdf will be downloaded.
Found this solution myself as I was facing issues at every step trying to download my notebook as pdf.
